Knowing the information of the security we want to know what would the market value for this security in the year 2019. For that, we need to know for how long we need to account for interest.

$$ \begin{aligned}
t & = 2019 - 2008\\
& = \boxed{11}
\end{aligned}\\

Now we compute the formula with the known values.


$$ \begin{aligned}
FV &= \$24,099\cdot{(1+0.0486)^{11}} \\
&= \boxed{\$40,616.96}
\end{aligned}$$

The price for this security in the NYSE 2019 should be of **$40,616.96**
